title: Puzzle Places Chicago Puzzle
description:
Maps are beautiful, but they are also fun. Puzzle Places (Like “puzzle pieces”… that are places…) are wood puzzles of your favorite city. Each piece has the neighborhood on it, so it’s both fun AND educational.

  • Dimensions: 13.125 x 19 in.
  • Pieces: 86 pieces
  • Loose cardboard backing, puzzle is a full cut-out frame
